model.environment.objects.physicalObject.sensor

Class XRaySystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.environment.map.MapComponent
      • model.environment.objects.physicalObject.PhysicalObject
        • model.environment.objects.physicalObject.sensor.XRaySystem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Openable, PolygonShape, DirectlyUpdatable, SimulationObject, Updatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicXRaySystem

    public abstract class XRaySystem
extends PhysicalObject
implements DirectlyUpdatable, Openable
    An X-Ray system is a system used at a checkpoint of an airport. It consists of an XRaySensor and some physical objects (i.e. conveyer belts) around it.
    Author:
    S.A.M. Janssen
